1
00:00:04,680 --> 00:00:05,680
[Previously]
Only after walking this path did I finally understand...

2
00:00:05,840 --> 00:00:06,519
It's not about how much you know.

3
00:00:06,520 --> 00:00:07,520
It doesn't make a person good.

4
00:00:07,680 --> 00:00:09,039
Proximity to vermilion makes one red, after all.

5
00:00:09,280 --> 00:00:10,919
That's why the Literary Sage

6
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:12,959
hopes Cui Dongshan can stay by your side.

7
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:15,159
Serve your teacher well on the journey home.

8
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:16,800
There will be plenty of rewards.

9
00:00:17,400 --> 00:00:18,439
The student asks:

10
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:20,159
"Crabs have six legs and two pincers"—

11
00:00:20,360 --> 00:00:21,399
Did I write that wrong?

12
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:24,079
The teacher replies:

13
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:25,440
A poor scholar...

14
00:00:25,840 --> 00:00:27,359
is always short on money.

15
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:30,079
If you're willing to truly protect
Bao Ping and the others,

16
00:00:30,320 --> 00:00:30,919
then I accept.

17
00:00:31,360 --> 00:00:32,360
You may become my student.

18
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:33,759
After all these twists and turns...

19
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:35,759
I've gained yet another teacher.

20
00:00:37,080 --> 00:00:38,479
A teacher must practice what he preaches.

21
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:39,359
You and I...

22
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:40,800
shall encourage each other.

23
00:00:46,080 --> 00:00:47,999
Li Bao Ping is simply lawless!

24
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:49,919
She actually drew a blade and beat three students...

25
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:51,519
One of them being

26
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:53,719
the precious son of Marquis Huaiyuan.

27
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:56,559
Who stole Li Huai's clay figure?

28
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:57,920
Hand it over!

29
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:00,159
Who hit Li Huai?

30
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:00,919
Step forward!

31
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:02,320
You there.

32
00:01:02,720 --> 00:01:03,759
Put down those straw sandals.

33
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:05,759
Fine then.

34
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,280
Kneel and beg me!

35
00:01:14,720 --> 00:01:15,799
The eldest legitimate grandson of the Chu clan

36
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:17,159
wanted to settle things with Li Bao Ping.

37
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,679
But on the way, he was beaten unconscious

38
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:20,159
by Lin Shou Yi.

39
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:23,319
A whole group ganging up on one little girl...

40
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:24,760
The students of Great Sui

41
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:26,359
are truly impressive.

42
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:29,519
Today I'll teach you mud-legged bumpkins
a lesson you'll never forget!

43
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,000
This is Great Sui,

44
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:32,560
not Great Li!

45
00:02:08,760 --> 00:02:10,359
When Lin Shou Yi was being beaten,

46
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,479
I didn't see anyone stopping it.

47
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,719
The way Young Master Pan acts

48
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:15,159
is no different from a mountain bandit.

49
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:20,919
You Great Li barbarians

50
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,319
dare to run wild here?

51
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:24,999
A sneak attack...

52
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,239
is indeed lacking in martial virtue.

53
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,759
But the ban on private brawls
has only just been issued.

54
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:29,599
So thank you very much.

55
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:31,799
You beat Young Master Pan
until blood flowed from all seven orifices.

56
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:34,039
Where is the scholarly grace in that?

57
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:34,999
What?

58
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,999
The sons of noble houses in yellow and purple
are allowed to fight,

59
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,719
but children studying far from home

60
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:39,999
can only suffer in silence?

61
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,879
What suffering?

62
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:43,480
These foreign students

63
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,359
have the teachers looking after their studies below,

64
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,799
and above, they even received precious gifts
personally bestowed by His Majesty.

65
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:50,439
On the contrary, it's the local students of Great Sui
who feel wronged.

66
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,200
Because of this incident,

67
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,879
the students who followed Elder Mao

68
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:56,119
when the old academy migrated from Great Li

69
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,919
have all taken Li Bao Ping's side.

70
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,319
They stand in sharp opposition to the local students.

71
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,839
Cliff Academy

72
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,519
is on the verge of splitting apart.

73
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:04,760
Absurd.

74
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,559
Elder Mao...

75
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,959
Say something!

76
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,119
Then...

77
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:12,079
so be it.

78
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:18,039
There must be someone behind this,
secretly fanning the flames.

79
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:21,719
Great Sui's enshrined tenth-realm Qi cultivator,
Cai Jingshen,

80
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,919
is still guarding the checkpoint at East Flower Mountain.

81
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,719
Is he simply too lazy to intervene,

82
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:28,639
or is he not allowed to?

83
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:31,559
Or perhaps the Great Li National Teacher
is secretly meddling,

84
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:34,199
stirring up trouble between the academy and Great Sui,

85
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:37,399
intending to completely sever

86
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,879
Cliff Academy's scholarly legacy.

87
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:39,319
Elder Mao...

88
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,679
The academy student Li Changying

89
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,319
personally went to apologize,

90
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:43,599
bearing the status of a Worthy and an imperial gift.

91
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,639
I heard that at Viewing Lake Academy

92
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:47,679
he passed the joint examination
of nine gentlemen

93
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,879
and obtained the title of Confucian Worthy.

94
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,399
Our Great Sui's Right Vice Minister of Rites

95
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,239
personally rode out ten miles from the city to welcome him.

96
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,479
And I also heard

97
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,759
that His Majesty ordered a senior eunuch

98
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,199
from the palace to deliver

99
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,039
a priceless set of the Four Treasures of the Study

100
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,199
as a token of commendation.

101
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,599
I hope this matter

102
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,359
ends here.

103
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,319
Any losses Young Master Lin suffered

104
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,839
I will compensate in full.

105
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:11,439
I have also collected quite a few
rare treasures.

106
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:12,880
I’ll deliver a few to Young Master Li

107
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,279
another day.

108
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,440
No need.

109
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,999
This young lady is both intelligent and brave,

110
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:20,319
truly possessing the spirit of a chivalrous heroine.

111
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,639
However, the academy

112
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,439
is not the jianghu where one acts on impulse.

113
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,559
I hope the young lady will turn hostility into friendship.

114
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,240
Changying

115
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,599
is deeply grateful.

116
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:36,679
How about this...

117
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,879
I’ll go apologize to them.

118
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,359
Apologize for what?

119
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:43,039
If Master and Little Shishu were here,

120
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,639
they’d be furious with you.

121
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,439
It was because of me that Lin Shouyi got hurt.

122
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,439
I know this matter isn’t over.

123
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,239
I’m not afraid of being beaten to death,

124
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,359
but if

125
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,839
you, Bao Ping, get hurt as well,

126
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,599
Chen Ping’an would never speak to me again in this life.

127
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,880
Li Huai...

128
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,959
If you’re not in the wrong, don’t apologize.

129
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:01,239
If Shishu were here,

130
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,519
he would say

131
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,839
“Li Huai, you are right.”

132
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:09,279
The academy is full of bad people.

133
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,519
If only Chen Ping’an were here...

134
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,399
Our Li Huai, General Li the Great...

135
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:17,519
crying so miserably.

136
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,359
If you can’t win, just endure it.

137
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,760
It’s not that big a deal.

138
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:26,760
No choice...

139
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,559
Even if you gave me the Xiangfu Blade,

140
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,319
I still couldn’t beat that Li Changying.

141
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,959
If Chen Ping’an were here,

142
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:40,639
what would he do?

143
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:45,719
Chen Ping’an would first reason with them properly.

144
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,159
After reasoning,

145
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,239
if the other party still refused to listen,

146
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,759
Little Shishu

147
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:52,119
would then use his fists to reason.

148
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:54,319
Now I understand.

149
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:56,359
What are you going to do?

150
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,000
On the way here,

151
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,399
Chen Ping’an always took the first half of the night watch,

152
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,639
and I took the second half.

153
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:01,839
That’s how it was before,

154
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:03,879
and that’s how it should be from now on.

155
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,040
When we reach Dragon Spring County,

156
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:10,039
Old Master, could you please not make me
do menial chores like making beds and sweeping?

157
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,239
If my brothers find out,

158
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,240
how embarrassing would that be?

159
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:16,159
How could I still be the big brother
to all those water ghosts and monsters?

160
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,439
I’m not bragging,

161
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,959
but if Old Master stops by my house on the way,

162
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:23,479
I’ll give you a grand welcome

163
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,919
with gongs, drums, and the river boiling over!

164
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,799
I didn’t control my strength well.

165
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:34,760
It’s fine.

166
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:36,599
To be honest with you,

167
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,519
that huge incident that shook Yellow Court Nation—

168
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:40,039
I took the blame for my water god brother.

169
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,279
I was chased for over two thousand miles

170
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,119
by the Supreme Elder of the Spirit Rhyme Sect.

171
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:44,639
Was I heroic?

172
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,679
Was I bold and gallant?

173
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:46,880
He was using you as a shield.

174
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,239
Do you really not know,

175
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,639
or do you know but simply don’t care?

176
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:52,119
What does a little girl like you know about brotherhood?

177
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:55,839
Daring to ruin my image in front of Old Master!

178
00:06:57,560 --> 00:07:00,399
Once I reach the town and eat that stone,

179
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:02,239
once my realm completely surpasses yours,

180
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,519
I’ll eat you too,

181
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,359
then shit you out later.

182
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:05,959
However, if you’re willing to warm the bed for Old Master,

183
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,879
I can consider sparing you.

184
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,319
Stop talking nonsense.

185
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,920
Old Master’s lesson is well taken.

186
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:13,879
Again.

187
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,200
Old Master...

188
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,400
Old Master,

189
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,839
what a fierce punch!

190
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:32,759
It’s almost on par with a tenth-realm martial artist.

191
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,120
Old Master,

192
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,959
considering how hard I worked feeding you punches

193
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:41,359
and even held back from eating that silly girl,

194
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,639
could you, Old Master,

195
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,040
once we get home,

196
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,519
give each of us one more snake gall stone?

197
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,359
Why does she get one too?

198
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,480
Then I want two!

199
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,720
Two stones, huh?

200
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:52,319
Yes.

201
00:07:53,367 --> 00:07:53,727
It’s all gone.

202
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,239
Old Master...

203
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:56,680
I know I was wrong.

204
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,239
One stone.

205
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,439
Just one stone.

206
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,879
A small token from your student.

207
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,479
I hope Master will graciously accept it.

208
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:07,519
Don’t worry.

209
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,319
These are just words on paper.

210
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,680
There’s no scheme behind them.

211
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,159
No need to help me.

212
00:08:13,520 --> 00:08:14,959
Just share some of the things
from your book box with me.

213
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:15,546
That’ll do.

214
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,279
Old Master...

215
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:20,479
I’m a fire python who’s lived for hundreds of years.

216
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,679
I can even carry an entire mountain on my back.

217
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,720
Old Master...

218
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:31,840
You’re so stingy.

219
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,719
At this rate, you’ll probably never find a wife.

220
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,639
Want me to help you take in a few concubines or maids?

221
00:08:37,208 --> 00:08:37,645
Don’t.

222
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,440
Old Master...

223
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,839
What if they don’t ask for any betrothal gifts

224
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,559
and even bring generous dowries?

225
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:45,119
Still not tempted?

226
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,199
Not tempted.

227
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,400
Why?

228
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,199
There’s already a girl I like.

229
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,879
With that personality of yours, Old Master...

230
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:00,359
The girl you like is probably a bit simple-minded.

231
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,080
Old Master...

232
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,679
How did you two meet?

233
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:04,959
Don’t tell me

234
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,599
you saved her, Old Master,

235
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,879
and even specially washed her clothes and cooked for her?

236
00:09:08,903 --> 00:09:15,903
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

237
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:18,359
So there are things even Ning Yao can’t do well.

238
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,199
Then there shouldn’t be such a thing as brewing medicine in this world.

239
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:25,880
If you want to laugh, just laugh.

240
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,879
Later, I ran into trouble.

241
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,400
Not only did she help me,

242
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,719
she even lent me her skirt-presser blade.

243
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,160
That was the most beautiful sight

244
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:36,799
I’ve ever seen in my life.

245
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,000
And then?

246
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:40,159
Then...

247
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:42,039
Then I returned the blade to her.

248
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:43,640
Old Master...

249
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,519
You’re such a blockhead.

250
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,639
Old Master...

251
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:57,399
How could anyone like you acting like this?

252
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,119
Even if an immortal from the mountain

253
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,519
tied a red thread between you two,

254
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:02,959
it still wouldn’t work.

255
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,039
Old Master...

256
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,400
Don’t mind it.

257
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,479
What if she really is a bit simple-minded?

258
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:15,639
[Clack]

259
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,439
Like a tortoise spotting a green bean—

260
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,520
they hit it off at first sight.

261
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:21,599
Old Master...

262
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:24,479
Actually, I’m quite good-looking too, you know.

263
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:27,919
Silly girl.

264
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,519
Quick, lend me some rouge and powder.

265
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:31,880
Disappear.

266
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,199
The night is long...

267
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:50,199
This lord has no desire to sleep.

268
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,799
A spring night is worth a thousand gold pieces.

269
00:10:55,216 --> 00:10:55,591
Silly girl.

270
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:58,079
How about you become my wife?

271
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:01,520
You stinking pervert!

272
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:03,399
What the hell?

273
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,639
This is a heaven-sent blessing!

274
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,839
Your ancestors’ graves are smoking with good fortune, you know?

275
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,639
You think I actually like you?

276
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:11,879
If I wasn’t coveting that snake gall stone of yours

277
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,439
that I haven’t even gotten yet...

278
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,639
You’re just relying on Old Master backing you up.

279
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:29,319
I wonder how Bao Ping, Li Huai, and Lin Shouyi are doing...

280
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,200
How are they?

281
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:36,919
You’re Yu Lu, right?

282
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:38,279
You were looking for me?

283
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:43,639
This is

284
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:45,039
the money for the medicine you bought.

285
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:45,999
If it’s not enough,

286
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,119
allow me to owe it for now.

287
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:48,519
Interesting.

288
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:51,439
But provoking me right after I apologized...

289
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:53,479
You had a tiny bit of reason on your side before,

290
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:55,199
but now you have none at all.

291
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,359
Someone who truly apologizes

292
00:11:58,760 --> 00:12:00,039
would never say something like that.

293
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,519
Rotten wood cannot be carved.

294
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:04,400
A wall of dung

295
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,720
cannot be plastered.

296
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:08,360
How fitting for you bunch of

297
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:09,359
Great Li

298
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,360
barbarians.

299
00:12:11,280 --> 00:12:12,280
According to that guy,

300
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,680
people like you

301
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,720
should be dealt with using fists.

302
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,240
Raise the formation!

303
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,559
Defending with sword cultivator techniques,

304
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:39,239
shifting with Daoist divine arts,

305
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:41,319
then meeting the enemy head-on with military combat skills.

306
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:42,999
Truly eye-opening.

307
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:29,600
A man without benevolence—

308
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,120
what use is ritual?

309
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,360
Still not stopping?

310
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:57,840
So young,

311
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,759
yet already so vicious at heart.

312
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:01,759
Li Huai’s clay figure still hasn’t been found.

313
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:04,559
Vile insults all poured into Li Bao Ping’s ears.

314
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:07,999
Despicable methods used against Lin Shouyi.

315
00:14:08,680 --> 00:14:09,839
And the ones who should apologize

316
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:11,720
haven’t let out

317
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:12,800
a single fart.

318
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,480
Fine.

319
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:15,959
This old man wants to see

320
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,799
whether you’ll still have any principles

321
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:19,759
once you’re lying on the ground.

322
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:22,720
Sixth-realm martial artist.

323
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,799
Out of respect for academy rules,

324
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,879
I’ll leave you half a life.

325
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:31,159
I’m begging you to be stronger.

326
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:47,319
You actually used me as a whetstone to break through?

327
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,840
You’re courting death!

328
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:04,920
My teacher has matters to attend to.

329
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:06,839
His disciple shall bear the burden.

330
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,000
Second Master Li.

331
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:18,920
A pleasure to meet you.

332
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:24,040
You surnamed Cui.

333
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:24,879
My son’s matter—

334
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:27,199
does it have anything to do with the schemes behind you?

335
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:28,319
It’s hard to say clearly.

336
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,119
Then I’ll beat you to death first.

337
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:31,399
Right now I’m only Cui Dongshan.

338
00:15:32,280 --> 00:15:34,399
I’m half a fellow disciple with your precious son.

339
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,319
You can’t just hit people recklessly.

340
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,519
Besides, Great Sui has deep foundations.

341
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:38,919
It cannot be—

342
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:39,359
It cannot be—

343
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,320
I’ll vent their anger for them.

344
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:42,920
Don’t do anything reckless.

345
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,599
Why don’t you go check on the children in the dormitory first?

346
00:15:46,560 --> 00:15:47,719
If I don’t do something,

347
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,000
as their father,

348
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:50,439
I won’t have the face to see my son.

349
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:53,719
Even until today,

350
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:56,079
not a single family elder behind those troublemakers

351
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,359
has said a word.

352
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:59,279
If you’re truly angry,

353
00:15:59,680 --> 00:16:01,599
you can go talk to their elders.

354
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:11,159
Mao Xiaodong.

355
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,399
Are you deliberately trying to disgust me?

356
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:14,319
Either go inside and pay your respects,

357
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:16,399
or make the matter clear.

358
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,879
Otherwise, the moment I see your face,

359
00:16:19,560 --> 00:16:20,359
I’ll be your grandson.

360
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:22,920
Xiaodong...

361
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:24,799
I came this time just to study properly,

362
00:16:25,040 --> 00:16:25,719
bask in the sun,

363
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,159
play a few games of chess with you,

364
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:29,359
and take care of those kids along the way.

365
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:31,079
All I know is

366
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:31,839
a dog

367
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:33,639
can’t change its habit of eating shit.

368
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,600
If you don’t believe me, fine.

369
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,000
The dirt on the wall—

370
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:38,159
do you want me to write a couplet for you?

371
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:42,559
Be careful—that might be your last words.

372
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:45,879
Heaven and man are separate.

373
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:48,119
Transform nature and arouse the artificial.

374
00:16:49,280 --> 00:16:50,280
The other line is:

375
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:51,960
Ritual establishes hierarchy.

376
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,280
Law reaches hegemony.

377
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:58,360
Not going to chat anymore?

378
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:00,639
Better wash your eyes quickly,

379
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,240
or you’ll go blind.

380
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:06,239
This youthful skin of mine

381
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:08,119
is truly capable of toppling kingdoms and cities.

382
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:11,319
For the sake of Teacher and Senior Brother,

383
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:12,599
I’ll trust you this once.

384
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:13,839
Cui...

385
00:17:14,280 --> 00:17:16,599
If you dare do anything that harms the academy,

386
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:18,200
even once,

387
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,999
I will personally kill you.

388
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:26,839
Great Sui’s intelligence network

389
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:28,079
is no worse than Great Li’s.

390
00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:31,479
Then I’ll act as an elder from Xie Xie’s sect.

391
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:47,439
Old man.

392
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,799
Your most proud disciple’s most proud disciple

393
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:51,000
has run into trouble.

394
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:53,199
And I’ve been entrusted with an important task by my own teacher.

395
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:55,279
You’re not going to show some appreciation?

396
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:56,479
That wouldn’t make sense, would it?

397
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:57,799
How about this—

398
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:59,199
lend me the third realm for a bit?

399
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,519
Old man, are you really going to ignore me?

400
00:18:04,080 --> 00:18:05,199
What kind of teacher are you?

401
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:06,400
You old bastard!

402
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,519
Did you hear that? I’m cursing you!

403
00:18:09,760 --> 00:18:10,839
Truly heartless and ungrateful.

404
00:18:13,280 --> 00:18:14,159
Fine, fine, fine. I’ll say it all.

405
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:16,039
Chen Ping’an, Li Bao Ping...

406
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:41,880
Golden Core realm.

407
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:43,079
Alright.

408
00:18:43,360 --> 00:18:44,360
You even gave me an extra realm.

409
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:48,559
Guess this Cui was blind.

410
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:50,639
From today on, this lord shall be called Cui Dongshan,

411
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,479
merely Chen Ping’an’s student.

412
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,119
Mom...

413
00:19:04,120 --> 00:19:05,120
Big Sister...

414
00:19:05,560 --> 00:19:07,279
I miss you both.

415
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:10,279
They bullied me too much.

416
00:19:11,520 --> 00:19:12,520
Yuan...

417
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:20,240
The earthworm eats the dust upon the green tendon.

418
00:19:23,520 --> 00:19:24,119
Cui...

419
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,200
Cui...

420
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:28,440
Happy?

421
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:29,760
Surprised?

422
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:37,920
Teacher didn’t come.

423
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:40,279
It’s just me, all alone and helpless.

424
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:44,399
Li Huai.

425
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:46,039
Chen Ping’an praised you for being brave

426
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:47,359
and responsible.

427
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:49,759
Said you’re a proper, upright young hero.

428
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:51,240
Really?

429
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:53,319
You idiot.

430
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:55,279
Would Little Shishu ever praise someone like that?

431
00:19:56,280 --> 00:19:59,079
At most, he’d just give you a thumbs up.

432
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:01,359
Little Shishu’s compliments

433
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:02,800
are all saved for me.

434
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:06,039
Teacher is naturally the best to Bao Ping.

435
00:20:06,840 --> 00:20:08,999
He specially caught a golden ridge-crossing crucian for you.

436
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:11,200
He said when we return home,

437
00:20:11,320 --> 00:20:12,559
he’ll have your big brother raise it for you first.

438
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:14,479
I was wondering...

439
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:18,239
With Teacher’s stingy temper that won’t even add extra oil or salt,

440
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,720
how come when it comes to you all,

441
00:20:19,800 --> 00:20:21,639
he suddenly stops treating treasures like treasures?

442
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,039
He’s not stupid either.

443
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:27,879
No no no no no!

444
00:20:28,520 --> 00:20:29,759
Chen Ping’an’s letter will arrive very soon.

445
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:31,079
He even specially instructed:

446
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:32,599
“My student Cui Dongshan

447
00:20:33,160 --> 00:20:34,160
is still a big scoundrel.

448
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:35,439
Don’t trust him no matter what.

449
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:37,039
But if you run into trouble,

450
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:38,999
you can ask him for help.”

451
00:20:43,360 --> 00:20:44,639
True jianghu chivalry

452
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:47,719
has never been about seeking momentary satisfaction.

453
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:49,319
The mountains are high and the rivers long.

454
00:20:49,320 --> 00:20:50,320
There will be plenty of time ahead.

455
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:51,960
If you make an enemy,

456
00:20:52,080 --> 00:20:53,359
first deal with the enemy himself,

457
00:20:53,840 --> 00:20:55,199
then bully his descendants.

458
00:20:56,120 --> 00:20:57,120
Remember that.

459
00:20:57,760 --> 00:20:59,159
For cultivators,

460
00:20:59,160 --> 00:20:59,599
whether seeking revenge

461
00:20:59,600 --> 00:20:59,959
or repaying kindness,

462
00:21:00,360 --> 00:21:01,799
a hundred years is not considered long.

463
00:21:03,183 --> 00:21:03,463
Hurry,

464
00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:05,280
Now that the serious matters are finished...

465
00:21:06,080 --> 00:21:07,519
Because my teacher was worried about you all,

466
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:09,759
he couldn’t truly calm his mind the entire journey.

467
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:10,799
So...

468
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,239
From now on,

469
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:14,719
you should all focus on your studies in peace.

470
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:16,720
Don’t worry about anything else.

471
00:21:17,040 --> 00:21:18,040
Leave the rest to me.

472
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:22,199
Young Master, forgive me.

473
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:24,319
Sit.

474
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:25,399
Tell me,

475
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:26,719
why did you step in to finish it?

476
00:21:28,720 --> 00:21:29,759
First, because I got impulsive

477
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:31,200
and just did it.

478
00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:32,999
Other mountains’ stones can polish jade.

479
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:34,160
I used the Great Sui sword cultivator

480
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:35,839
as a whetstone for my own martial path.

481
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:37,920
Continue.

482
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:42,799
Otherwise,

483
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:44,200
I’ll say it for you.

484
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:45,680
As long as I don’t die,

485
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:46,639
in the future Chen Ping’an

486
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:48,119
will feel he owes me a favor.

487
00:21:48,320 --> 00:21:49,320
Young Master previously said

488
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,119
that Xie Xie and I

489
00:21:50,520 --> 00:21:52,479
are ten thousand miles apart in temperament from Chen Ping’an.

490
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:54,279
We could never be friends in this life.

491
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:55,879
I know Young Master

492
00:21:56,040 --> 00:21:57,040
is most likely right.

493
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:57,999
But I’m not willing to accept it.

494
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:59,200
I wanted to try.

495
00:21:59,320 --> 00:22:01,279
I just never expected Young Master would turn back.

496
00:22:02,040 --> 00:22:03,040
Please punish me, Young Master.

497
00:22:03,520 --> 00:22:04,719
Killing three birds with one stone.

498
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:05,799
Well done!

499
00:22:06,320 --> 00:22:07,519
I’m so happy I can barely contain myself.

500
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:08,880
Why would I punish you?

501
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:14,880
Young Master...

502
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:15,960
Aren’t you afraid your identity will be exposed?

503
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,559
Using killing to stop killing.

504
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:19,719
Using evil to control evil. Got it?

505
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:23,599
You two, pick one person to leak the information.

506
00:22:25,160 --> 00:22:26,799
For example, Xie Lingyue from the Wind God Xie clan.

507
00:22:28,040 --> 00:22:29,759
Then I’ll appear as an elder from her sect.

508
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:31,759
If it’s you,

509
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:34,399
then I’ll be one of the hidden gatekeepers of the Lu Dynasty.

510
00:22:35,080 --> 00:22:36,839
Give Great Sui a seemingly absurd reason

511
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:38,200
to intervene reasonably.

512
00:22:38,360 --> 00:22:39,439
Just beat them into submission.

513
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:43,240
Pick me.

514
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:44,919
Cherish the fairer sex.

515
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:48,719
Don’t think you’ve already seen through me.

516
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,159
Be careful—one leaf can block your eyes.

517
00:22:51,160 --> 00:22:53,199
But if you can see clearly into the deepest depths,

518
00:22:53,760 --> 00:22:54,760
that would be even better.

519
00:22:56,040 --> 00:22:56,679
You should know

520
00:22:57,040 --> 00:22:59,039
this is actually one of my Great Daos.

521
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:01,199
One of Cui the National Teacher’s Great Daos.

522
00:23:01,680 --> 00:23:02,680
How could it be small?

523
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:05,079
If someone truly sees through this single leaf

524
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:06,599
and perceives the greater whole from the small,

525
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:08,199
would it really still blind them?

526
00:23:10,800 --> 00:23:11,119
Time to loosen up my muscles and bones.

527
00:23:11,120 --> 00:23:12,120
Loosen up my muscles and bones.

528
00:23:15,120 --> 00:23:17,399
That old turtle bastard Cai Jingshen—

529
00:23:18,040 --> 00:23:19,319
hurry up and come recognize your ancestor!

530
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:21,359
Your eighteenth-generation ancestor

531
00:23:21,840 --> 00:23:23,799
is here today to teach you family rules and ancestral precepts.

532
00:23:24,280 --> 00:23:25,799
Go bathe and change your clothes quickly.

533
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:27,679
Kneel and listen to the lecture.

534
00:23:37,080 --> 00:23:38,479
Who the hell is courting death?

535
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:41,319
Your old ancestor is looking for his turtle grandson.

536
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:43,399
That’s not courting death.

537
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,479
Get the hell out here!

538
00:23:57,040 --> 00:23:58,040
Good grandson.

539
00:23:58,360 --> 00:24:00,279
Hurry up and roll inside.

540
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:03,480
Where did this madman come from?

541
00:24:03,800 --> 00:24:04,800
Die!

542
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:27,520
Cai Jingshen.

543
00:24:27,760 --> 00:24:28,760
Make it quick and clean.

544
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:30,279
Hurry up and slit your own throat.

545
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:32,199
Make sure you do it with sincerity.

546
00:24:33,120 --> 00:24:34,759
Who the hell lent you the dog胆 to

547
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:37,079
dare bully this old man’s disciples?

548
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:41,400
Not bad, you have some skill.

549
00:24:41,840 --> 00:24:42,840
Come again.

550
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,240
What the hell is this?

551
00:24:49,520 --> 00:24:50,919
This is horse piss from your ancestor.

552
00:24:51,320 --> 00:24:52,320
Still coming?

553
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:53,600
You madman!

554
00:24:53,760 --> 00:24:54,959
Don’t think I won’t kill you.

555
00:25:00,120 --> 00:25:01,120
Well done!

556
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:03,559
My good grandson finally knows how to show filial respect to his ancestor.

557
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:11,079
You brat want to die?

558
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:12,879
Then this old man will send you on your way.

559
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:17,920
Nice spear.

560
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:19,200
Your ancestor will take it for you.

561
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:20,720
You’d better live long enough to claim it.

562
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,160
Overestimating yourself.

563
00:25:30,520 --> 00:25:31,919
It is impolite not to reciprocate.

564
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:33,400
A gift from your old ancestor.

565
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,159
Grandson Cai Jingshen,

566
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,319
catch it properly.

567
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:37,119
What?

568
00:25:37,560 --> 00:25:38,560
Porcelain?

569
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:39,680
A ritual robe?

570
00:25:40,280 --> 00:25:41,639
Who the hell are you exactly?

571
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:44,159
You still dare talk back to your ancestor?

572
00:25:44,320 --> 00:25:45,320
Slap your own mouth!

573
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:47,879
If I speak this Great Immortal’s name,

574
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:49,160
I’m afraid it’ll scare you to death.

575
00:25:49,560 --> 00:25:50,479
Turtle grandson Cai Jingshen,

576
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,480
listen obediently to the lecture.

577
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:55,199
The Cai family temple enshrines a clay statue.

578
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:56,959
Incense smoke produced a stinky pickled vegetable.

579
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:58,879
Suddenly an ancestor descends from beyond the heavens.

580
00:25:58,880 --> 00:26:00,399
In panic, three bags were changed at the door.

581
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:02,319
Trying to cover it with wind and thunder.

582
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:03,999
Instead, the spear tip lifted the piss cover.

583
00:26:04,160 --> 00:26:06,079
With tenth-realm cultivation bullying the young and weak,

584
00:26:06,080 --> 00:26:07,759
shameless, cunning, and rotten.

585
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:09,759
If not for angering your ancestor into coming,

586
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:11,439
I’d scold you for being both useless and shameless.

587
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:13,199
You don’t even know your mistake, nor do you repent.

588
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:14,799
Today you shall receive your lesson.

589
00:26:14,800 --> 00:26:16,599
With no merit, no virtue, and no face,

590
00:26:16,600 --> 00:26:17,999
you still dare clamor in front of the formation.

591
00:26:18,040 --> 00:26:19,239
Rarely does your ancestor have free time,

592
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,639
hands itchy and body strong.

593
00:26:20,840 --> 00:26:22,279
Then I shall curse my grandson a hundred times.

594
00:26:22,280 --> 00:26:23,280
A hundred times!

595
00:26:23,560 --> 00:26:24,560
Bullshit!

596
00:26:24,840 --> 00:26:25,879
You noisy little brat,

597
00:26:26,160 --> 00:26:27,199
stop acting so arrogantly!

598
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:28,640
Mao Xiaodong!

599
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:30,119
Is your academy not going to control this madman?

600
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:32,199
Then Cai Jingshen will handle him for you.

601
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:34,439
You just need to collect the corpse.

602
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:38,400
My teacher doesn’t have many...

603
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:39,840
Now there’s only one.

604
00:26:40,560 --> 00:26:42,159
Not many fellow disciples catch my eye.

605
00:26:42,600 --> 00:26:43,639
Not many close friends.

606
00:26:43,960 --> 00:26:45,159
Not many beauties worth a second glance.

607
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:47,319
But I sure have plenty of magic treasures.

608
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:53,159
Today I’ll properly teach this unfilial grandson a lesson.

609
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:13,159
Bullying my son like this...

610
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:14,959
Damn your mother, Great Sui!

611
00:27:14,983 --> 00:28:18,883
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

